  "142": {
    "inputs": {
      "text": "大远景俯拍，深秋雨夜的老旧桥洞下，陈峰蜷缩在两个浸透雨水的蛇皮袋之间，衣衫紧贴身躯，发梢滴落的水珠凝滞在半空，面部被冷蓝逆光勾勒出清晰轮廓，皮肤纹理与每一根湿黏的胡茬纤毫毕现，身后城市霓虹在积水中碎裂成幽蓝光斑，雨幕如银线垂落，车流低鸣的震动隐于空气，整幅画面笼罩在湿冷的寂静中,手里拿着手机，photorealistic, ultra-detailed, 8k uhd, sharp focus, natural lighting, real skin texture, hyperrealism, professional photography, RAW photo\n﻿\n||| The scene may contain natural text on any of the following: signs, billboards, labels, stickers, posters, graffiti, product packaging, paper notes, screens (digital or phone), t-shirts, badges, license plates, chalkboards, banners, or neon displays. All such text must be clearly readable, high-resolution, realistic typography, with every letter or character complete and correctly formed. No gibberish, no missing strokes, no corrupted or unreadable symbols. The text should look authentic to the context (e.g., a shop name, a warning label, a price tag, a slogan).\n﻿\nNo watermarks, no logos, no signatures, no brand names, no captions, no subtitles, no UI text, no timestamp overlays. Surfaces are clean from extraneous artificial markings.",
